              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "heading",
              "settings": {
                "title": "President, Amerigroup International | President & Founder, AmerigroupLNG | Founder of AmeriGas Propane S.A. de C.V.",
                "header_size": "h5",
                "align": "center",
                "title_color": "#2563eb",
                "typography_font_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 13, "sizes": [] },
                "typography_font_weight": "600",
                "_padding": { "unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "12", "left": "0", "isLinked": false }
              },
              "elements": []
            },
            {
              "id": "tm1bio",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Mr. Gerardo Payán Ramos serves as President in Amerigroup International, Founder and CEO of AmerigroupLNG, as well as the founder of AmeriGas Propane S.A. de C.V. in Mexico. With over 15 years in the energy industry, he is steering these companies toward becoming leading global providers of integrated energy solutions. His journey began as a consultant for Coca-Cola bottling companies across Latin America. Specializing in government relations and strategic partnerships between Mexico and the USA, Gerardo has become an authority in emerging energy fields — ranging from LNG and hydrogen to solar, wind, and EV conversion.</p>",
                "typography_font_size": { "unit": "px", "size": 14, "sizes": [] }
              },
              "elements": []
            }
          ]
        },

