              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Mr. James Wang, CEO for China at Amerigroup International, steers the company's strategic vision and operations in the Chinese market. With over 15 years of experience at Fortune 500 companies and leading Chinese corporations, he excels in managing government relations and partnering with state-owned enterprises. He has overseen transactions exceeding $10 billion and played a key role in Belt and Road projects across several African countries.</p>",
