            {
              "id": "tm4bio",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p>Mr. Roberto Compeán Woodworth, CFO of Amerigroup International for the Mexico region and co-founder of AmerigroupLNG, drives the company's financial strategy. His leadership includes Chief Sales Officer at Mexico's National Lottery and CFO for Bestel and Cablevision Monterrey — key Televisa subsidiaries. His tenure at BBVA Bank, including advanced training in Madrid, solidified his expertise in finance. He earned his Bachelor's in Business Administration from ITAM University.</p>",
